<DATE_TIME> 1998-03-25 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Xinhua Home News Digest (at 24:45 Beijing Time, March 24) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
-- Chinese President Jiang Zemin meets visiting Harvard
University President Neil Rudenstine.
</P>
<P>
-- President Jiang Zemin meets a Belarussian parliamentary
delegation.
</P>
<P>
-- Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji will attend the second
Asia-Europe Meeting in London from April 3 to 4. Besides, Zhu will
visit the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland
from March 31 to April 2 and France, from April 5 to 7.
</P>
<P>
-- Mozambican President Joaquim Alberto Chissano will pay a
state visit to China from March 28 to April 4.
</P>
<P>
-- Premier Zhu Rongji urged State Council members to treasure
power entrusted by the people.
</P>
<P>
-- Harvard scholars seek deeper understanding of China.
</P>
<P>
-- China's central bank announces new interest rate reduction.
