<HEADLINE> 3 Terrorists Captured Dead in Myanmar </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, March 25 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar authorities Wednesday
confirmed that three terrorists were captured dead in Haka,
capital of Chin state, Northwest Myanmar last Saturday.
</P>
<P>
They were captured together with two handguns, one hand grenade
and two mines at a distance of 3.3 kilometres west of Haka, an
official information sheet said.
</P>
<P>
"The terrorists intended to disrupt the annual Student Sports
Festival which is to be held at the national level in Chin state
in the coming week for the year 1998," it said. 
</P>
