General Technology Group Holding Ltd. wholly owns four powerful
subsidiary companies, each with more than 10 years of experience
in foreign trade.
</P>
<P>
-- The People's Bank of China, the nation's central bank, has
announced that the interest rates on bank loans and deposits
will be lowered as of today.
</P>
<P>
The bank began reforming the deposit reserve fund system on
March 21, and will reduce interest rates on loans and deposits
granted to financial institutions.  
